N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 170.5 - Principal business address

State Regulations

All licensees under article 7 of the General Business Law
shall maintain a principal place of business within New York State which shall
contain the employee and business records for any licensed activities conducted
within New York State. Notes
